. We supported <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bpaindia.org\/\">Blind People&#8217;s Association<\/a><\/strong>, an organization providing equal opportunities to the specially challenged with the aim to spread happiness and share joy.<\/p>\n<p>The beautiful thing about the initiative was that members from every community came forward to help and support the cause in whatever way they could. This initiative also helped us realize that happiness multiples when shared with others.<\/p>\n<p>On the eve of Dhanteras, Gozoom Technologies team visited Blind People\u2019s organization to personally distribute essential items to the specially challenged. After all, what better occasion for spreading lights and transforming lives of people than Diwali, the festival of lights.<\/p>\n<p>The gala celebrations continued at office. Entire Gozoom Technologies office was decorated with diyas and stunning rangolis.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3180\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/01_collage.jpg\" alt=\"01_collage\" width=\"720\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/01_collage.jpg 720w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/01_collage-300x146.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>It was great to see the technology savvy developers and designers create magic with their artistic abilities. The beautiful spirit of the celebrations and contagious energy made this yet another event to cherish for lifetime.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Every year, the Gozoom Technologies family celebrates Diwali, the festival of lights by illuminating the lives of people. Last year, we joined hands with Special Need Education Home (SNEH) a special home for differently-abled children. This year was no different. Continuing our tradition of contributing to the society and ma